The paper discusses strategies for training deep models sequentially on a single incremental task, which is a common problem in machine learning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning and deep learning, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Among these, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories, as they are broad categories that encompass many topics related to machine learning and deep learning. The other categories are also relevant, as they relate to specific applications of deep learning, such as computer vision and natural language processing.
